Butterknife provisioning image
==============================

We're using Buildroot to generate all-in-one (<15MB) provisioning image
which can be either booted via PXE or from a USB memory stick.

Steps to reproduce the image:

  git clone http://git.buildroot.net/git/buildroot.git
  patch -p1 < ../path/to/buildroot/patches/*.diff

To tweak the build:

  make menuconfig
  make linux-menuconfig
  make busybox-menuconfig

Make sure you:

* Enable packages: jq pv fdisk btrfs-progs find dialog
* Make sure you use fdisk from util-linux, not from busybox.
* Make sure you enable support for necessary ethernet cards and SATA controllers 

To compile the image run:

  make

